Package: projectoR
Title: Create and Manage Structured Research Projects
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Hauke", "Roggenkamp", , "hauke.roggenkamp@unisg.ch", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides tools for creating standardized, reproducible research project structures. Supports organizing multiple studies within a single project, with automatic directory scaffolding, literate programming workflows (.qmd files), traditional R scripts, git integration, and bibliography management. Designed to promote best practices in research reproducibility and project organization.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
